abstract: Google must face a Wisconsin company’s lawsuit over a toolbar feature that generates Web links from search data, a federal appeals court decided.
snippet: Google must face a Wisconsin company’s lawsuit over a toolbar feature that generates Web links from search data, a federal appeals court decided.
lead_paragraph: Google must face a Wisconsin company’s lawsuit over a toolbar feature that generates Web links from search data, a federal appeals court decided in a ruling posted on Wednesday.

headline.main: Appeals Court Reinstates Patent Suit Against Google
headline.print_headline: Appeals Court Reinstates Patent Suit Against Google
